'''歐洲圍棋大會'''（European Go Championship）是由{{link-en|歐洲圍棋聯盟|European Go Federation}}舉辦的[[圍棋|圍棋]]競賽。歐洲圍棋大會包括2週的公開競爭，每天一輪，總共10輪比賽產生最終冠軍新興。歐洲圍棋大會每年在不同[[歐洲|歐洲]][[城市|城市]]舉行<ref>{{cite book|last=Botermans|first=Jack|title=The Book of Games: Strategy, Tactics & History|publisher=Sterling Publishing|isbn=978-1-4027-4221-7|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=6mqF71_8x44C&pg=PA325|location=New York|page=325|year=2008|access-date=2016-03-03|archive-date=2014-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140701191111/http://books.google.com/books?id=6mqF71_8x44C&pg=PA325|dead-url=no}}</ref>，1983年第一屆歐洲圍棋大會舉辦<ref>{{cite web |title=European Go Congresses |url=http://www.eurogofed.org/history/congress.htm |website=www.eurogofed.org |accessdate=2019-05-06 |archive-date=2012-09-08 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6AWQyblAE?url=http://www.eurogofed.org/history/congress.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

